    {
      "parameters": { "content": "## Client Offboarding\n\nTrigger: an **Offboard Client** button on a CRM row (Send webhook). Tick **Company, Name, Email, Projects** so the workflow can find the linked project.\n\nWhat it does: sets the client to ⭐ Alumni, sends a wrap-up email, and (if a project is linked) marks it ✅ Complete + Offboarded and creates testimonial + asset-archival tasks.\n\nReplace `<<YOUR_TASKS_DATABASE_ID>>` and attach your Notion + SMTP credentials.", "height": 320, "width": 420, "color": 4 },
